Installation

Pre-Reqs

python     3.*
django     1.8 or >
yara-python

pip	install django mysqlclient
pip install django
pip install python-memcached
pip install django-admin-bootstrapped
pip install yara
pip install Pillow
pip install django-dual-authentication


DataBase

The default is to use a sqlite file

To use another database engine modify settings.py and modify the database section accordingly

git clone https://github.com/kevthehermit/YaraManager

cd YaraManager

./manage.py makemigrations rule_manager

./manage.py migrate

./manage.py createsuperuser

# Username Must be in email address format e.g. username@domain.com It does not need to be valid.

./manage.py runserver 

./manage.py runserver 0.0.0.0:9191